<% provide(:title, "Game Tracker - Mobile Apps for Football, Basketball and Soccer") %>
<p>
<div class="row">
	<div class="col-xs-12">
		<div class="well">
			<h4 class="text-info">Sponsors or fans can purchase ads and support your program from our GameTracker app or the web.</h4>
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-xs-6">
					<h5>Purchase an ad using GameTracker</h5>
					<%= image_tag 'fanapp/InAppAdList.png', class: 'img-responsive' %>
				</div>
				<div class="col-xs-6">
					<h5>Purchase an ad using GameTrackerPro.com</h5>
					<%= image_tag "fanapp/AdInventoryImage.png", class: 'img-responsive' %>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="col-xs-12">
		<div class="well">
			<h4 class="text-info">Step one - Administrator of the sports program creates ad inventory. Pick the price points that you think your supporters will pay for. Keep in mind that GameTracker will take <%= Admin.first.adpercentage %>%.</h4>
			<%= image_tag "fanapp/AdInventoryImage.png", class: 'img-responsive' %>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="col-xs-12">
		<div class="well">
			<h4 class="text-info">Step two - A sponsor enters their info, chooses an ad level and uploads their digital media .....</h4>
			<%= image_tag "fanapp/ad-enter-info.png", class: 'img-responsive' %>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="col-xs-12">
		<div class="well">
			<h4 class="text-info">Step three - Sponsors purchase the ad on your site .....</h4>
			<h5 class="text-success">Paypal is used to maximize your ad revenue. It is possible to allow purchase of ad inventroy from mobile devices but Apple and Google will take a 30% of the total. That's a big hit when you factor in the GameTracker revenue split of <%= Admin.first.adpercentage %>%!</h5>
			<%= image_tag "fanapp/ad-paypal-payment.png", class: 'img-responsive' %>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="col-xs-12">
		<div class="well">
			<h4 class="text-info">Step four - Sponsors can change their info or update their digital media at any time .....</h4>
			<%= image_tag "fanapp/adinfo-upload.png", class: 'img-responsive' %>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="col-xs-12">
		<div class="well">
			<h5 class="text-info">Advertisers can choose not to upload digital media. Your team logo will be used instead of sponsor supplied digital media if no digital media is uploaded.</h5>
			<h5 class="text-info">Advertisers may also choose to upload a custom banner for display on mobile devicesor they can also choose to allow GameTracker to create a banner automatically.</h5>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
